briefdescription.para: MainWindow::MainWindow.

parameterdescription.para: Creates the mainwindow, gets current time for print log, loads and initializes saved settings and initializes plot

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::~MainWindow Called when the main window is closed.
MainWindow::showError helper function to show the appropriate API Error message.

parameterdescription.para: - I - error messgae to be shown

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::on_ManualStage_clicked Open the manual stage control window, sends home command to stage and closes mainwindow connection.
MainWindow::on_SetSliceThickness_clicked Sets m_PrintSettings.LayerThickness variable from the value inputted by the user.
MainWindow::on_SetStageVelocity_clicked Sets StageVelocity variable from the value inputted by the user, also directly sends command to stage to set velocity.
MainWindow::on_SetStageAcceleration_clicked Sets StageAcceleration variable from the value inputted by the user, also directly sends command to stage to set acceleration.
MainWindow::on_SetMaxEndOfRun_clicked Sets MaxEndOfRun variable from the value inputted by the user, also directly sends command to stage to set max end of run.
MainWindow::on_SetMinEndOfRun_clicked Sets MinEndOfRun variable from the value inputted by the user, also directly sends command to stage to set min end of run.
MainWindow::on_SetExposureTime_clicked Sets ExposureTime variable from the value selected by the user.
MainWindow::on_SetUVIntensity_clicked Sets UVIntensity from the value selected by the user.
MainWindow::on_SetDarkTime_clicked Sets DarkTime variable from the value selected by the user.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList1_activated.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList2_activated.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList3_activated.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList4_activated.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList5_activated.
MainWindow::on_LiveValueList6_activated.
MainWindow::on_ResinSelect_activated.

parameterdescription.para: The resin selected Prints the resin selected to the terminal

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::on_InitializeAndSynchronize_clicked Prepares the system for printing, moves stage to starting position inits plot, uploads images to the light engine.
MainWindow::on_StartPrint_clicked Starts print process, set LED current calculates speed for continuous motion mode.
MainWindow::on_StageConnectButton_clicked Connects to stage, if succesful gets position, sends home commands and gets position.
MainWindow::on_LightEngineConnectButton_clicked Connect to light engine, gets last error code to validate that no errors have occured and connection is working.
MainWindow::on_SelectFile_clicked Select all object image files to project.
MainWindow::on_ClearImageFiles_clicked Clear image files selected.
MainWindow::ExposureTimeSlot Handles all dark time actions required.
MainWindow::DarkTimeSlot Dummy slot, may be removed.
MainWindow::saveText Saves Terminal Window printout to .txt log upon print completion or abort.
MainWindow::on_LogFileBrowse_clicked Select directory to store log files.
MainWindow::on_SetStartingPosButton_clicked Sets Starting Position variable from the value inputted by the user (also doubles as debug tool for GetPosition(), will be removed)
MainWindow::on_AbortPrint_clicked Aborts print and acts as e-stop. Stops light engine projection, stage movement and print process.
MainWindow::on_SetIntialAdhesionTimeButton_clicked Sets InitialExposure variable from the value inputted by the user.
MainWindow::on_AutoCheckBox_stateChanged.

parameterdescription.para: The state of the AutoCheckBox If AutoCheckBox is set, go into auto mode

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::on_setPrintSpeed_clicked Sets PrintSpeed variable from value inputted by user, also triggers automode.
MainWindow::on_pushButton_clicked Opens the Manual Pump Control window and closes the mainwindow pump connection.
MainWindow::on_PumpConnectButton_clicked Connects to pump.
MainWindow::on_GetPosition_clicked Gets position, saves it in module level variable GetPosition, updates slider and prints to terminal window.
MainWindow::on_SetMaxImageUpload_clicked Sets the max image upload, used to avoid large error buildup or large wait times due to large uploads.
MainWindow::on_SetPrintHeight_clicked Sets PrintHeight variable from value inputted by user, also triggers automode.
MainWindow::on_AutoCheckBox_clicked Guard on edge case that sets the checkbox while it's actual state is unchecked.
MainWindow::on_UsePrintScript_clicked Used to select whether to use set print variables or print script.

MainWindow::on_SelectPrintScript_clicked User selects print script from file, the print script is parsed and the exposure time and LED intensity is stored in module level QStringLists: ExposureScriptList and LEDScriptList.
MainWindow::on_ClearPrintScript_clicked Clears selected print list.
MainWindow::on_ImageProcess_clicked Opens the image processing window.
MainWindow::on_POTFcheckbox_clicked Sets projection mode to POTF.
MainWindow::on_VP_HDMIcheckbox_clicked Sets projection mode to Video Pattern.
MainWindow::Check4VideoLock Validates that the video source is locked, this is needed for Video Pattern Mode.
MainWindow::on_DICLIPSelect_clicked Preps the system for use with iCLIP printer.
MainWindow::on_SetBitDepth_clicked Sets the module variable BitMode which is used to determine the bit depth the user wishes to print with.
MainWindow::on_SteppedMotion_clicked Sets motion mode to stepped, this is the default.
MainWindow::on_ContinuousMotion_clicked Sets motion mode to continuous.
MainWindow::on_pumpingCheckBox_clicked Enables pumping mode in which the stage movement is exaggerated to avoid the part sticking to the window.
MainWindow::on_setPumping_clicked Sets the pumping depth parameter.
MainWindow::pumpingSlot Pumping slot for when pumping is activated, intermediary step between exposure time and dark time.
MainWindow::on_CLIPSelect_clicked Preps the system for use with the 30 um printer.
MainWindow::on_SetInfuseRate_clicked.
MainWindow::on_SetVolPerLayer_clicked.
MainWindow::on_ContinuousInjection_clicked.
MainWindow::updatePlot Updates current plot with new stage position.
MainWindow::ValidateSettings.

simplesect.para: bool: true if settings are valid, false otherwise

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::loadSettings Loads the settings from file to module variables.
MainWindow::saveSettings Saves settings so that they are initialized upon startup.
MainWindow::initSettings Updates the UI to reflect the settings.
MainWindow::initPlot Initializes live plotting of stage position.
MainWindow::initConfirmationScreen.

simplesect.para: bool: true if user has confirmed, false otherwise Initializes the confirmation screen so that the user can confirm whether the input parameters are correct

briefdescription.para: MainWindow::AutoMode Calculates exposure time and slice thickness based on input print height and print speed.
MainWindow::initImagePopout Initializes the image popout window that is used for video pattern mode.
MainWindow::VP8bitWorkaround Used as a workaround for the exposure clipping seen in Video Pattern mode due to Bit Blanking.

simplesect.para: Validating printscript to avoid segmentation faults
